CHARM MONSTER

Usage       : cast 'charm monster' <victim>
Accumulative: No
Duration    : (432/Intelligence points of monster) hours

Very similar to charm person, but allows you to charm monsters too.
In addition to the level restriction, monsters with a great deal of health
will scoff at your attempt to charm them.

The master of a charmed monster is responsible for its actions.  Keep your
pets from doing anything illegal - see Hall of Rules.  Charm's are made to
do things through the ORDER command.

See Also: CHARM PERSON, ORDER
Related Topics: SPELL INFO
